# The Integrator

The Integrator helps work groups and departments to have a method of organizing static websites to meet the individual customized needs of a department or any type of group.

The organizer is a static website deployed on github so it's reach is global by default at no cost.

The organizer is fast and easy to update or change the format of at any time.

All changes can be tracked in github version control system for quick rollback if necessary and for reviewing changes that were made in the past.
